title: Next Generation of Back-UPS Overview – BE600M1 and BE850M2
description: Power and protect all of your critical electronics while maintaining your internet connection during prolonged outages. The new and improved APC Back-UPS™ keeps you connected to what matters the most by providing more runtime and battery backup outlets than ever before. This video features the BE600M1 (replacing the BE550G) and the BE850M2 (replacing the BE750G).
